# 🧠 PanjoCoin (PNJC) — Protocol Architecture Specification v1.0

## 🛡️ Institutional-Grade System Design (CertiK-Level Documentation)

---

# 1. 📌 System Overview

PanjoCoin (PNJC) is a modular DeFi protocol deployed on Polygon consisting of five core subsystems:

* **Token Layer** — PNJC ERC-20 core asset
* **Distribution Layer** — Airdrop + Vesting engine
* **Yield Layer** — Staking reward system
* **Liquidity Layer** — Router + DEX interaction logic
* **Governance Layer** — Multisig control system

The system is designed as a **non-upgradable token core with modular external financial logic**.

---

